window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>For the last 20 years, Cid has served the realm as a city guard.</p> <p>One thing has driven him forward. A suggestion by a friend.</p> <p>His eventual pension and what he plans to do with it.</p> <p>A purchase.</p> <p>Specifically in the village of Haven and the plot of land reserved by the Kingdom.</p> <p>After a lifetime of fights and scuffles, it's time for something new.</p> <p>Time to be....</p> <p>A farmer.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p> <p>Pick up a copy of <i>Mana Harvest</i> and enjoy the listen!</p>"; 
